  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "Minimal-profile UnitOfAssurance for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. Thirteen credibility factors assessed under ASME V&V 40-2018 at Model Risk Level 5. hasContextOfUse is intentionally absent; intended-use scope is undefined (W-ON-01).",
