    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL-5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed; all achieved levels fall below required levels. Six factors remain unassessed and are flagged as epistemic gaps. Despite these deficiencies the package is formally accepted at this review stage pending remediation plan submission. No context of use has been recorded in this minimal-profile submission.",
